{"While none of us has a perfect crystal ball and we don't know the path this virus might take, I could really not be prouder of how our teams across Comcast Cable, NBCUniversal and Sky are together managing our business."}

翻译为中文：

{"虽然我们之中没有人拥有完美的水晶球，我们也不知道这个病毒可能走的路线，但我真的非常骄傲我们Comcast Cable、NBCUniversal和Sky的团队一起管理我们的业务。"}
